er.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哈姆雷特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />羅密歐與茱麗葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主你個名點讀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c40b1676551cf825c73502e3fed4f46c5c423a","tid":169704,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>李爾王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />奧賽羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哈姆雷特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />羅密歐與茱麗葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主你個名點讀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主網名釋讀：<br />\n<br />\n龘、靐、齉、齾、龗、麤、鱻<br />\n<br />\n粵音分別讀若：<br />\n踏、並、nong6、亞、靈、粗、鮮<br />\n<br />\n字義：<br />\n龘：形容詞。龍飛的狀態。<br />\n靐：形容詞。例詞：靐靐，形容雷聲。<br />\n齉：形容詞。鼻塞。<br />\n齾：（一）作名詞用：本義為缺齒，引申義為缺漏、事物欠缺遺漏之處。又可指野獸吃剩的東西。（二）作動詞用：特指器物缺損，破損，亦指一般的缺損、殘缺。又可引申為挫損，使（積極性、上進心等）遭受損傷。<br />\n龗：名詞。上古一種龍的名字，義即「龍」。或讀若龍。<br />\n麤：形容詞。「粗」之異體字；義同「粗」。<br />\n鱻：形容詞。「鮮」之異體字；義同「鮮」。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b3ee530ca1e363f208a592c029b58385f3349e8b","tid":169704,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:57:01.000Z","msg":"King Lear"},{"pid":"f4a28f9328a8293ae65d571fd509fa36078b18f4","tid":169704,"uid":25530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"堅尼米拿"},{"pid":"ab1eec0de218fb24846201e69896a3b820573b31","tid":169704,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"我讀英國文學"},{"pid":"d4d9fbde373d462f0b5f653821941fbbdc29b981","tid":169704,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T11:46:49.000Z","msg"